$ VBA: option explicit

`option explicit` requires variables to be declared with → development/languages/VBA/language/statements/dim[`dim`].

sa:
  → development/languages/VBA/language/statements

  VBScript's → development/languages/VBScript/language/option-explicit[`option explicit`].

  A *rough* equivalent of `option explicit` in → Windows/PowerShell is the cmdLet → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/strictMode/set[`set-strictMode`].
